overview: "Gray's Anatomy" meets "Swingers" in this medical comedy as medical intern Ron Wilson plots to become Chief Resident with the help of Ivy League reject Steven Powell. As Dr. Wilson fights for survival in a busy county hospital, he has to decide whether becoming Chief Resident is more important than personal happiness. Together with Steve they set off on adventure and mayhem.
tagline: If they're not committing malpractice, then they're not working fast enough.
title: Hula Gods
